reviewText: The VCTF continues to look for Jack of all Trades but gets stumped again. Amazing how inept they are. Sam Watters charecter starts to grind away on you as she is so uncomfortable and uneasy in day to day conversations. Many of the stroy lines seem to blend togwther.
Title: Profiler - Season 2

reviewText: I loved this show and had a lot of the shows taped on VHS.  When we finally got rid of the VHS player, I really did not think I would be able to find this show on DVD's.  I was happily surprised to find them here at Amazon.  I have found that Amazon either gets things to you immediately or else it is quite a while.  I did have to wait a long while - I kept getting notices that it was out of stock - to receive this, but it was worth the wait as I can once again enjoy the shows.
Title: Profiler - Season 2

reviewText: This season is just as good as the first season and the stories are well thought out. I hear that season three is not as good but I will probably get it to finish the set. Great Series !!
Title: Profiler - Season 2

reviewText: LOVE THIS SERIES; ONE OF THE BEST; GREAT CHARACTERS, SUSPENSE DRAMA AND ALL WE CAN WATCH IN A TV SERIES; VERY EXCITING...HOW I MISS THIS KIND OF SHOWS!!! IM STILL WATCHED AND FEEL THE SAME WAY AS WHEN I WATCHED FOR THE FIRST TIME...BUY IT!!
summary: ONE OF THE BEST TV SERIES; LOVE IT...
